[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "すみませ～ん！\n市民の皆様、どいてくださ～～～い！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00159",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "おばさんＡ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "タイニーちゃん、また遅刻かい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_697_036_00160",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "おばさんＢ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "すっかりこの辺りの名物だねぇ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_698_036_00161",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "うぅ、一度は起きたのに！\n食後、精神集中したら、そのまま夢世界へ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00162",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "頑張って私、今日は入国審査の当番なんだよ！\nここで遅刻したらボスの大目玉が……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00163",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "おじさん",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "頑張れタイニーちゃん、\n本部の門はまだ開いてるぞ～！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_699_036_00164",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ほ、本当ですか！？　情報感謝であります！\nよ、よかったあぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00165",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あああぁぁぁあああぁっ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00166",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "おじさん",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おお、痛そう、顔面から地面に……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_699_036_00167",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "い、つつ……メガネ、メガネ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00168",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ここにあるぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00169",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あ、ありがとうございます～\nどこのどなたか存じませんが、幸あらんことを～……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00170",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00171",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボ、ボス！？　すすすすすすみません！！\n反省文２０枚を提出する所存ゆえ何とぞ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00172",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "タイニー。お前は何者だ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00173",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "か、監察官見習いのタイニー・ロンパイであります！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00174",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "監察官とはなんだ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00175",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "は、はっ！　監察官は、諸島同盟の秩序を守る使命を\n帯びた公僕であります！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00176",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "一般市民からすれば、我々は等しく監察官だ。\n見習いという言葉に甘んじるのはやめろ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00177",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "い、一刻も早く市民に頼られる\n誇り高き監察官になるよう、精進いたします！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00178",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "その心がけを忘れるな。\nさあ、やることはたくさんある。行くぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00179",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はいっ、ボス！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00180",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "おじさん",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "タイニーちゃん、頑張れよ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_699_036_00181",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "近々ベスティラへ監査に入る。\n出張になるから準備をしておけ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00182",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ベスティラ……獣人の島ですよね？\nそれはまたどうして……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00183",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "詳細は追って伝える。\nだが、下された命令の真意を測るのはいいことだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00184",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "その調子で自分で考え、動ける監察官になれ。\nいいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00185",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "えへへ。今の、ほめてくれたんですよね？\nいくつになっても、ほめられると嬉しいものですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00186",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "とにかく準備しておきます！　ベスティラかぁ。\n遠いなあ……遠方出張、緊張する～……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00187",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "やっ、監察官のデコボコ師弟さん。\nご機嫌はいかがー？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00188",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あ、変てこ仮面さん。おはようございます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00189",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "変てこねぇ……俺にはジョゼ・ダンブロシオという\n名前があるんだから、覚えてよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00190",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "でも、変てこな仮面してますし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00191",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "賞金稼ぎは顔を覚えられたらいけないのさ。\n賞金首にお礼参りされちゃうからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00192",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "船から降りてきたということは、仕事帰りか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00193",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ、たんまり稼いできたよ。\n１杯くらいならおごってもいいけどー？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00194",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "仕事中だ。そんなに暇ならこちらの仕事を手伝え。\nなんなら、監察官になれるよう手配してもいい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00195",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺を高く買ってくれるのはありがたいけどさ、\n規律に縛られるのはごめんなんでね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00196",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "いつも思いますけど、ボスって変てこ仮面さんへの\n評価高いですよね～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00197",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "腕前と嗅覚は確かだからな。私は実績を評価する",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00198",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それじゃ俺はこれで。ああ、そういえば。\nなんだか面白そうな船が港に来てたよー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00199",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あ、さようなら～。お元気で、変てこ仮面さん！\n飲みすぎ食べすぎには注意してくださいねー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00200",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "……行っちゃいましたね。\nなんでしょう？　面白そうな船って……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00201",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ジョゼは軽口は多いが、落とす情報は確かだ。\n港に様子を見に行くぞ。これも監察官の仕事だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00202",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "は、はいっ！　あぁっ、口と足が同時に動いている。\n待ってくださーい！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00203",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "タイニー・ロンパイ",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny Rompuy",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "諸島同盟監察官の見習い。\n明るく優しい性格で、よく年上にかわいがられている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "エルス・マーティン",
		"romanized_name": "Els Martin",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "諸島同盟監察官の女性。\n厳しい仕事ぶりが知られている、タイニーの上司",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ・ダンブロシオ",
		"romanized_name": "José d'Ambrosio",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "諸島同盟で活動している、正体不明の賞金稼ぎ。\nタイニーによくちょっかいをかけている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]